程序包 hdb.data.nonrelational

类 DataObject

java.lang.Object
hdb.data.nonrelational.DataObject
所有已实现的接口:
java.io.Serializable
public class DataObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
A DataObject represents an entity using a number of attributes organized possibly in a hierarchical fashion. DataObjects in a non-relational collection can have different sets of attributes.
作者:
Jeong-Hyon Hwang (jhh@cs.albany.edu)

    • DataObject

      public DataObject​(CollectionSchema schema, java.io.ObjectInputStream in) throws java.io.IOException, java.lang.ClassNotFoundException, CollectionSchema.InvalidAttributeIndexException
      Constructs a DataObject from the specified ObjectInputStream.
      参数:
      schema - a CollectionSchema
      in - an ObjectInputStream
      抛出:
      java.io.IOException - if an I/O error occurs
      java.lang.ClassNotFoundException - if the class of a serialized object cannot be found
      CollectionSchema.InvalidAttributeIndexException - if an attribute not registered in the CollectionSchema is read
